OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA showery
OL,6,Fevening with some heavy and thundery
OL,7,Fshowers possible. Showers continuing
OL,8,Fovernight although begin to ease a
OL,9,Flittle towards dawn. Turning chilly in
OL,10,Fthe countryside but mainly frost-free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mix of sunny spells and some
OL,13,Fwell scattered showers. Cloud building
OL,14,Flater with some wet and windy weather
OL,15,Farriving during the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,18,Fclearing Tuesday to a mix of sunshine
OL,19,Fand blustery showers. Further showers
OL,20,Fpossible on Wednesday, then turning
OL,21,Fdrier, brighter and warmer on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
